{"rule_id":"RULE-GENERAL-001","knowledge_type":"rule","title":"多数工业 PID 回路应先按稳健性整定再逐步提速","plant_type":"any","industry_tags":["chemical","oil_gas","power","water_treatment","hvac","pharma","food_beverage","metallurgy","manufacturing"],"loop_type":"any","control_target":"any","model_types":["FO","FOPDT","SOPDT","IPDT","NEAR_INTEGRATING"],"risk_tags":["process_variation"],"summary":"如果对象增益、滞后或工况代表性仍有不确定性，应优先采用稳健整定，再依据闭环表现逐步提高速度。","recommendation_level":"recommended","preferred_strategy":["LAMBDA","IMC","conservative_pi"],"discouraged_strategy":["aggressive_pid"],"suggested_actions":["prefer_robust_parameters","validate_in_shadow_mode"],"rollback_advice":"如果上线后行为不确定，优先回退到更保守参数。","operator_note":"先求稳，再提速。","source":"generic_pid_expert_graph"}
{"rule_id":"RULE-GENERAL-002","knowledge_type":"rule","title":"执行器问题未排除前不应把整定问题误判为参数问题","plant_type":"any","industry_tags":["chemical","oil_gas","power","water_treatment","hvac","manufacturing"],"loop_type":"any","control_target":"any","model_types":["FO","FOPDT","SOPDT","IPDT"],"risk_tags":["saturation","stiction","deadband"],"summary":"卡涩、饱和、死区和分辨率不足会直接改变闭环行为，应先确认执行器健康度，再讨论是否增强 Kp、Ki 或 Kd。","recommendation_level":"recommended","preferred_strategy":["conservative_pi"],"discouraged_strategy":["aggressive_pid"],"suggested_actions":["check_valve","reduce_kp","limit_ki"],"rollback_advice":"执行器问题未解决前不要继续提速。","operator_note":"先修执行器，再调 PID。","source":"generic_pid_expert_graph"}
{"rule_id":"RULE-GENERAL-003","knowledge_type":"rule","title":"采样周期长或滤波过重时应降低整定激进度","plant_type":"any","industry_tags":["chemical","water_treatment","hvac","pharma","manufacturing"],"loop_type":"any","control_target":"any","model_types":["FOPDT","SOPDT","IPDT"],"risk_tags":["measurement_delay","slow_sampling"],"summary":"采样周期过长或滤波过重会增加表观时滞，整定应降低激进度并谨慎使用 D。","recommendation_level":"recommended","preferred_strategy":["LAMBDA","conservative_pi"],"discouraged_strategy":["strong_derivative","aggressive_pid"],"suggested_actions":["reduce_kd","add_filter","limit_ki"],"rollback_advice":"若闭环反应迟钝且抖动并存，先检查采样与滤波设置。","operator_note":"数字采样本身就是动态约束。","source":"generic_pid_expert_graph"}
{"rule_id":"RULE-TEMP-GEN-001","knowledge_type":"rule","title":"换热器出口温度回路通常优先 PI 或弱 D PID","plant_type":"heat_exchanger","industry_tags":["chemical","power","hvac","food_beverage"],"loop_type":"temperature","control_target":"outlet_temperature","model_types":["FOPDT","SOPDT"],"risk_tags":["thermal_inertia","coupling"],"summary":"换热器出口温度受热容和流量扰动影响，D 项收益通常有限，优先采用 PI 或弱 D PID。","recommendation_level":"recommended","preferred_strategy":["PI","IMC"],"discouraged_strategy":["strong_derivative"],"suggested_actions":["prefer_pi","reduce_kd"],"rollback_advice":"若阀门动作频繁或温度噪声偏高，优先削弱 D。","operator_note":"热工对象更重视平稳性。","source":"generic_pid_expert_graph"}
{"rule_id":"RULE-TEMP-GEN-002","knowledge_type":"rule","title":"反应釜温度在放热或强非线性场景下应按最敏感工况保守整定","plant_type":"reactor","industry_tags":["chemical","pharma"],"loop_type":"temperature","control_target":"reactor_temperature","model_types":["FOPDT","SOPDT"],"risk_tags":["nonlinear_gain","process_variation"],"summary":"放热反应和负荷变化会显著改变有效增益，整定宜按最敏感工况保守设置。","recommendation_level":"recommended","preferred_strategy":["LAMBDA","IMC"],"discouraged_strategy":["aggressive_pid"],"suggested_actions":["reduce_kp","limit_ki","prefer_robust_parameters"],"rollback_advice":"负荷切换后若波动增大，优先回退到稳健参数。","operator_note":"反应器先看最危险工况。","source":"generic_pid_expert_graph"}
{"rule_id":"RULE-TEMP-GEN-003","knowledge_type":"rule","title":"锅炉主汽压力回路应偏快但避免燃料阀和风门频繁动作","plant_type":"boiler","industry_tags":["power"],"loop_type":"pressure","control_target":"main_steam_pressure","model_types":["FO","FOPDT"],"risk_tags":["coupling","actuator_wear"],"summary":"主汽压力回路通常要求较快响应，但不应因参数过强造成燃料阀、风门或给煤量频繁波动。","recommendation_level":"recommended","preferred_strategy":["PI","IMC"],"discouraged_strategy":["over_aggressive"],"suggested_actions":["moderate_kp","gentle_ki","watch_actuator_frequency"],"rollback_advice":"若执行器动作频次过高，先降低比例。","operator_note":"压力要快，但设备磨损要可控。","source":"generic_pid_expert_graph"}
{"rule_id":"RULE-LEVEL-GEN-001","knowledge_type":"rule","title":"汽包液位回路应优先保障库存缓冲而非单纯追求液位快速回归","plant_type":"steam_drum","industry_tags":["power"],"loop_type":"level","control_target":"drum_level","model_types":["IPDT","FOPDT"],"risk_tags":["inventory","shrink_swell"],"summary":"汽包液位兼具库存和平衡特性，过快整定容易把蒸汽扰动和给水波动进一步放大。","recommendation_level":"recommended","preferred_strategy":["conservative_pi"],"discouraged_strategy":["aggressive_pid"],"suggested_actions":["keep_kp_low","reduce_ki"],"rollback_advice":"若给水阀动作过大或液位波动变快，优先收紧 PI。","operator_note":"液位不是越快越好。","source":"generic_pid_expert_graph"}
{"rule_id":"RULE-PH-001","knowledge_type":"rule","title":"pH 中和回路在中性点附近应显著降低激进度","plant_type":"ph_neutralization","industry_tags":["chemical","water_treatment","pharma","food_beverage"],"loop_type":"ph","control_target":"ph_value","model_types":["FOPDT","SOPDT"],"risk_tags":["nonlinear_gain","measurement_delay"],"summary":"pH 回路在中性点附近过程增益变化剧烈，沿用远离中性点的参数往往过于激进。","recommendation_level":"recommended","preferred_strategy":["LAMBDA","conservative_pi"],"discouraged_strategy":["aggressive_pid"],"suggested_actions":["reduce_kp","reduce_ki","prefer_robust_parameters"],"rollback_advice":"靠近中性点若振荡加剧，应立即降低比例和积分。","operator_note":"pH 回路必须尊重强非线性。","source":"generic_pid_expert_graph"}
{"rule_id":"RULE-FLOW-GEN-001","knowledge_type":"rule","title":"泵站管网压力回路在多泵切换工况下应重新评估增益","plant_type":"pump_station","industry_tags":["water_treatment","oil_gas","hvac"],"loop_type":"pressure","control_target":"network_pressure","model_types":["FO","FOPDT"],"risk_tags":["process_variation","coupling"],"summary":"多泵并联或切泵会改变管网增益与动态，切换后不应机械沿用原参数。","recommendation_level":"recommended","preferred_strategy":["IMC","conservative_pi"],"discouraged_strategy":["reuse_old_parameters_without_check"],"suggested_actions":["reidentify","reduce_kp"],"rollback_advice":"切泵后如出现振荡，优先回退并重新辨识。","operator_note":"泵切换后对象常常已经变了。","source":"generic_pid_expert_graph"}
{"rule_id":"RULE-PRES-GEN-001","knowledge_type":"rule","title":"压缩机出口压力回路整定应服从保护边界和执行器动作约束","plant_type":"compressor","industry_tags":["oil_gas","chemical","manufacturing"],"loop_type":"pressure","control_target":"discharge_pressure","model_types":["FO","FOPDT"],"risk_tags":["saturation","coupling"],"summary":"压缩机导叶、回流阀或转速执行器存在动作限制，整定应优先服从保护边界而不是极限速度。","recommendation_level":"recommended","preferred_strategy":["PI","IMC"],"discouraged_strategy":["aggressive_pid"],"suggested_actions":["moderate_kp","limit_ki","check_actuator_limits"],"rollback_advice":"接近保护边界时不要继续强化参数。","operator_note":"先保设备，再谈响应速度。","source":"generic_pid_expert_graph"}
{"rule_id":"RULE-HVAC-001","knowledge_type":"rule","title":"送风温度回路受季节和负荷变化影响明显时应保留稳健裕度","plant_type":"ahu","industry_tags":["hvac","semiconductor","pharma"],"loop_type":"temperature","control_target":"supply_air_temperature","model_types":["FOPDT","SOPDT"],"risk_tags":["process_variation","coupling"],"summary":"送风温度回路受室外气象、负荷和阀门开度范围影响，宜采用保守 PI 并预留重新整定机制。","recommendation_level":"recommended","preferred_strategy":["PI","IMC"],"discouraged_strategy":["aggressive_pid"],"suggested_actions":["keep_kp_conservative","limit_ki"],"rollback_advice":"季节切换后若控制品质下降，应重新评估参数。","operator_note":"暖通对象要考虑全年工况漂移。","source":"generic_pid_expert_graph"}
{"rule_id":"RULE-HVAC-002","knowledge_type":"rule","title":"静压回路若末端风阀频繁动作则不应继续增强比例","plant_type":"ahu","industry_tags":["hvac","semiconductor"],"loop_type":"pressure","control_target":"static_pressure","model_types":["FO","FOPDT"],"risk_tags":["coupling","actuator_wear"],"summary":"末端风阀联动频繁说明系统耦合和执行器负担上升，主静压回路不应继续提高比例。","recommendation_level":"recommended","preferred_strategy":["PI"],"discouraged_strategy":["over_aggressive"],"suggested_actions":["reduce_kp","watch_actuator_frequency"],"rollback_advice":"阀门频繁扫动时优先收紧主回路。","operator_note":"不要让主回路逼着末端一起抖。","source":"generic_pid_expert_graph"}
{"rule_id":"RULE-MFG-001","knowledge_type":"rule","title":"电机转速回路可较快整定但需警惕编码器噪声和机械共振","plant_type":"motor_drive","industry_tags":["manufacturing","metallurgy","paper"],"loop_type":"speed","control_target":"motor_speed","model_types":["FO","SOPDT"],"risk_tags":["high_noise_risk","mechanical_resonance"],"summary":"转速对象通常响应较快，但编码器噪声、机械共振和驱动限幅会限制可用增益。","recommendation_level":"recommended","preferred_strategy":["PI","PID"],"discouraged_strategy":["strong_derivative"],"suggested_actions":["allow_higher_kp","reduce_kd","check_resonance"],"rollback_advice":"若出现高频抖动或共振，优先降低比例并去掉 D。","operator_note":"快对象也要尊重机械边界。","source":"generic_pid_expert_graph"}
{"rule_id":"RULE-MFG-002","knowledge_type":"rule","title":"张力回路应把卷径或工艺阶段视为关键工况实体","plant_type":"web_tension_system","industry_tags":["paper","manufacturing","food_beverage"],"loop_type":"tension","control_target":"web_tension","model_types":["FO","FOPDT"],"risk_tags":["process_variation"],"summary":"卷径变化会直接改变有效增益和惯性，张力回路不宜在全工况范围内固化单一激进参数。","recommendation_level":"recommended","preferred_strategy":["gain_scheduled_pi","conservative_pi"],"discouraged_strategy":["reuse_old_parameters_without_check"],"suggested_actions":["reidentify","prefer_robust_parameters"],"rollback_advice":"卷径变化后若品质变差，应切换到对应参数区间。","operator_note":"张力参数必须和卷径绑定看。","source":"generic_pid_expert_graph"}
{"rule_id":"RULE-MFG-003","knowledge_type":"rule","title":"伺服位置回路存在结构共振或齿隙时不应盲目增强 D 项","plant_type":"servo_axis","industry_tags":["manufacturing","semiconductor"],"loop_type":"position","control_target":"servo_position","model_types":["SOPDT"],"risk_tags":["mechanical_resonance","backlash","high_noise_risk"],"summary":"结构共振、齿隙和编码器噪声会使 D 项放大高频问题，不能把增加 D 当作通用补救手段。","recommendation_level":"recommended","preferred_strategy":["PI","weak_pid"],"discouraged_strategy":["strong_derivative"],"suggested_actions":["reduce_kd","add_filter","check_mechanical_clearance"],"rollback_advice":"若位置环高频抖动，先降低 D 再排查机械问题。","operator_note":"位置环的问题常不只是参数问题。","source":"generic_pid_expert_graph"}
{"rule_id":"RULE-WATER-001","knowledge_type":"rule","title":"水处理池液位回路应优先承担缓冲功能","plant_type":"tank","industry_tags":["water_treatment","chemical","food_beverage"],"loop_type":"level","control_target":"tank_level","model_types":["IPDT","FOPDT"],"risk_tags":["inventory"],"summary":"池罐液位回路承担流量缓冲功能，不宜为了局部液位误差快速归零而放大上下游波动。","recommendation_level":"recommended","preferred_strategy":["conservative_pi"],"discouraged_strategy":["aggressive_pid"],"suggested_actions":["keep_kp_low","reduce_ki"],"rollback_advice":"若上下游流量波动被放大，应进一步降低积分。","operator_note":"库存调节的第一目标是缓冲。","source":"generic_pid_expert_graph"}
{"rule_id":"RULE-WATER-002","knowledge_type":"rule","title":"溶解氧回路在采样慢和扰动频繁时应更保守","plant_type":"aeration_basin","industry_tags":["water_treatment"],"loop_type":"dissolved_oxygen","control_target":"dissolved_oxygen","model_types":["FOPDT","IPDT"],"risk_tags":["slow_sampling","process_variation"],"summary":"溶氧测量和生化过程响应较慢，曝气量扰动频繁时不宜采用激进整定。","recommendation_level":"recommended","preferred_strategy":["LAMBDA","conservative_pi"],"discouraged_strategy":["aggressive_pid"],"suggested_actions":["limit_ki","prefer_robust_parameters"],"rollback_advice":"若曝气阀频繁大幅动作，应先收紧积分。","operator_note":"慢测量对象宁可保守。","source":"generic_pid_expert_graph"}
{"rule_id":"RULE-SCENARIO-001","knowledge_type":"rule","title":"模式切换或批次切换后不应直接固化旧 PID 参数","plant_type":"any","industry_tags":["chemical","pharma","food_beverage","manufacturing"],"loop_type":"any","control_target":"any","model_types":["FO","FOPDT","SOPDT","IPDT"],"scenario_tags":["mode_switch","batch_switch"],"risk_tags":["process_variation"],"summary":"模式切换和批次切换通常意味着对象动态改变，旧 PID 参数应重新评估后再决定是否沿用。","recommendation_level":"recommended","preferred_strategy":["conservative_pi","LAMBDA"],"discouraged_strategy":["reuse_old_parameters_without_check"],"suggested_actions":["reidentify","temporary_use_only"],"rollback_advice":"切换后性能变差时优先回退稳健参数。","operator_note":"工况一变，经验也要重新验。","source":"generic_pid_expert_graph"}
{"rule_id":"RULE-RISK-006","knowledge_type":"rule","title":"存在逆响应或非最小相位特征时应显著降低整定激进度","plant_type":"any","industry_tags":["chemical","power","hvac","manufacturing"],"loop_type":"any","control_target":"any","model_types":["FOPDT","SOPDT"],"risk_tags":["inverse_response"],"summary":"逆响应对象在初期方向与最终方向不一致，过强比例和积分会显著放大闭环风险。","recommendation_level":"recommended","preferred_strategy":["LAMBDA","conservative_pi"],"discouraged_strategy":["aggressive_pid"],"suggested_actions":["reduce_kp","limit_ki"],"rollback_advice":"若初期反向动作明显，应进一步收紧参数。","operator_note":"逆响应对象必须先稳后快。","source":"generic_pid_expert_graph"}
{"rule_id":"RULE-RISK-007","knowledge_type":"rule","title":"存在明显死区或分辨率不足时不应继续增强积分","plant_type":"any","industry_tags":["chemical","oil_gas","power","hvac","manufacturing"],"loop_type":"any","control_target":"any","model_types":["FO","FOPDT","SOPDT","IPDT"],"risk_tags":["deadband","quantization"],"summary":"死区和分辨率不足会制造假性稳态误差与往复动作，继续增强积分通常会恶化极限环。","recommendation_level":"recommended","preferred_strategy":["PI","conservative_pi"],"discouraged_strategy":["aggressive_integral"],"suggested_actions":["reduce_ki","check_actuator_limits"],"rollback_advice":"存在明显锯齿波动时先检查分辨率和死区。","operator_note":"很多积分问题其实是执行器分辨率问题。","source":"generic_pid_expert_graph"}
